{"tid":1217427,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大附屬學院校長陳龍生：欣賞學生真誠 尊重你們選擇","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:44:26.000Z","uid":96182,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa4d4eaf8b54482cfae9d93b13a126f4570bbae","tid":1217427,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"面對送中條例引發新一輪佔領，10間大學校長昨發出聲明呼籲各方冷靜，但未有直接評論學生行為。香港大學附屬學院（HKU SPACE Community College）校長陳龍生今日發出的聲明，明顯較正面地肯定學生所為，明言「欣賞你們的真誠和尊重你們的選擇（appreciate your sincerity and respect the path of action you have chosen to take）」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳龍生向全校學生發電郵，開首表示見到心愛的城市充滿混亂，橡膠子彈和催淚彈射向學生和年輕人，令人感到悲傷。他稱學院管理層非常關注金鐘的惡化情況，並特別關注有份參與的學生的安全。<br />\n陳續說，明白當政府使市民失望，市民可能會覺得他們有權透過嚴厲的方法確保他們的聲音得以聆聽（I understand that when a government fails its people, people may think they have the rights to resort to rigorous means to ensure their voices are heard）。對於有份參與的學生，他欣賞其真誠和尊重其選擇，但亦提醒他們要留意可能出現的後果，並要時刻留心自己的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f4bc47af6a6a241143da10e36299888666fdd7","tid":1217427,"uid":213424,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"space校長屌打hku"},{"pid":"3216edeea5f6c902eabcb5296103ae1249b89031","tid":1217427,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58dd720fda10e13f7d13679c9d6024fbe445864","tid":1217427,"uid":202170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"然後唔笑太